powerpc: make memremap_compat_align 64s-only

memremap_compat_align is only relevant when ZONE_DEVICE is selected.
ZONE_DEVICE depends on ARCH_HAS_PTE_DEVMAP, which is only selected
by PPC_BOOK3S_64.

